filolials in the world.

204
00:12:19,608 --> 00:12:21,233
My name is Fitoria.

205
00:12:22,983 --> 00:12:24,442
Nice to meet you.

206
00:12:26,817 --> 00:12:28,525
[MELTY]
Fitoria?

207
00:12:28,608 --> 00:12:29,483
