capital after a diplomatic trip.

245
00:13:42,442 --> 00:13:46,025
[NAOFUMI] I see. So that's
something you do often?

246
00:13:46,108 --> 00:13:47,608
Anyway, not that I'm ungrateful

247
00:13:47,692 --> 00:13:49,900
